* {{msg-mw|picturegame-create-threshold-comment-score-plus}}
* {{msg-mw|picturegame-create-threshold-comment-score-minus}}
* {{msg-mw|picturegame-create-threshold-recruits}}
* {{msg-mw|picturegame-create-threshold-friend-count}}
